web.errors.why_is_this_secret_unavailabl.text: He aha tēnei karere huna kāore e wātea?

web.errors.secrets_are_designed_to_be_vi.text: Kua hoahoatia ngā karere huna kia kitea kotahi noa te wā. Kua urunga pea tēnei hononga, kua pau, kua mukua ā-ringa rānei e te kaituku.

web.errors.contact_the_person_who_sent_y.text: Whakapā atu ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga, ā, tonoa ki te waihanga i tētahi karere huna hou. Kia mōhio rātou kāore koe i taea te uru ki ngā mōhiohio taketake.

web.errors.oops_the_page_you_are_looking.text: Auē! Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei.

web.errors.if_youre_unsure_what_to_do_ne.text: Mēnā kāore koe e tino mōhio me aha koe ā muri ake nei, tēnā whai ake ki te tangata nāna i tuku tēnei hononga mō ētahi atu mōhiohio.

web.errors.information_shared_through_ou.text: Ko ngā mōhiohio i tuari mā tā mātou ratonga ka taea te uru kotahi anake. Ka tirohia ana, ka mukua pūmautia te ihirangi mai i ā mātou tūmau hei whakaū i te noho muna. Ka āwhina tēnei huarahi ki te tiaki i ō raraunga tairongo mā te whakawhāiti i tōna whakaaturanga me te ārai i te urunga whakaaetia-kore.

web.errors.were_sorry_but_an_unexpected_.text: E whakapāha ana mātou, engari i puta he hapa ohorere i te wā o te tukatuka i tō tono. Kua whakamōhiotia tō mātou rōpū, ā, kei te mahi mātou ki te whakatika.

web.errors.go_share_a_secret.text: Haere tuari i tētahi karere huna!

web.errors.the_page_youre_looking_for_do.text: Kāore te whārangi e rapu ana koe i te tīari, kua nekehia rānei. Kaua e māharahara, ka pā tēnei ki te pai rawa o tātou!

web.errors.unable_to_load_data_due_to_da.text: Kāore e taea te uta raraunga nā ngā take whakatakotoranga raraunga. Tēnā ngana anō ā muri ake.
